book.part:
        Anyframe Monitoring Tool


			Anyframe provides a Monitoring Tool collecting data for measuring performance 
			with Aspect and reporting data analysis result based on InfraRED. 
			InfraRED is an open source for monitoring JavaEE based application performance. 
			Next, looked into are installation of and how to use Monitoring Tool. 

